00:28:59,740 --> 00:29:02,060
 my redeemer lives.

663
00:29:02,060 --> 00:29:05,100
 In the midst of pain and anguish, physical ailment,

664
00:29:05,100 --> 00:29:06,820
 my redeemer lives.

