00:29:06,820 --> 00:29:10,100
 When you lose a loved one, my redeemer lives.

666
00:29:10,100 --> 00:29:12,900
 You see, that is our hope, that Jesus Christ,

667
00:29:12,900 --> 00:29:16,580
 the seed of the woman, he lives, he's our hope.

668
00:29:16,580 --> 00:29:18,680
 It's this very same hope,

669
00:29:18,680 --> 00:29:21,260
 which has been held onto for millennia.

