00:29:21,260 --> 00:29:23,680
 The prophets all wrote of it, they spoke of this hope.

671
00:29:23,680 --> 00:29:26,100
 Many people have waited for thousands of years

672
00:29:26,100 --> 00:29:27,340
 for this hope.

673
00:29:27,340 --> 00:29:30,020
 Now we have him, we have this hope.

674
00:29:30,020 --> 00:29:33,300
 Yet unlike all the people of God that came before us,

675
00:29:33,300 --> 00:29:35,560
 we don't have to wait and look forward to it.

676
00:29:35,560 --> 00:29:37,880
 We look back to something that already happened.

677
00:29:37,880 --> 00:29:40,520
 We know what happened, we have a confidence of it,

678
00:29:40,520 --> 00:29:42,880
 of the time that Jesus entered the world

679
00:29:42,880 --> 00:29:46,640
 to live a perfectly righteous life that we never could.

680
00:29:46,640 --> 00:29:49,080
 To suffer and die a painful, humiliating death

