00:30:17,900 --> 00:30:21,480
 Not only is this a present reality that we look back to,

692
00:30:21,480 --> 00:30:23,080
 that we commemorate yearly,

693
00:30:23,080 --> 00:30:27,100
 we also have an even greater future hope that we hold onto.

694
00:30:27,100 --> 00:30:30,180
 The second advent, the second coming of Jesus Christ

695
00:30:30,180 --> 00:30:33,360
 into the world, the Messiah who will once and for all

